#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "CDDA Variety Pack"
msgstr "CDDA 多樣化包"

#. ~ Description for CDDA Variety Pack
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds vehicle variants (extended cab / bed pickups, for example), and some "
"QoL fixes so you can drink during winter. Also adds some character creation "
"options regarding gender, sexuality."
msgstr "添加車輛變體（例如加長駕駛室/貨箱的皮卡），以及一些生活質量修復，讓你在冬季也能飲水。同時添加了一些關於性別、性取向的角色創建選項。"

#: .\items\insulated_jerrycan.json
msgid "insulated jerrycan"
msgid_plural "insulated jerrycans"
msgstr[0] "絕緣油桶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'insulated jerrycan'}
#: .\items\insulated_jerrycan.json
msgid "A bulky plastic jerrycan with insulation."
msgstr "一個帶有絕緣層的笨重塑料油桶。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: male or mostly male"
msgstr "性別：男性或主要為男性"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: male or mostly male'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "You express yourself in a conventionally masculine way."
msgstr "你以傳統男性化的方式表達自己。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: female or mostly female"
msgstr "性別：女性或主要為女性"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: female or mostly female'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "You express yourself in a conventionally feminine way."
msgstr "你以傳統女性化的方式表達自己。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Trans"
msgstr "性別：跨性別"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Trans'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Trans-male'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Trans-female'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "You don't express the gender assigned at birth."
msgstr "你不表達出生時被指定的性別。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Non-Conforming"
msgstr "性別：非傳統"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Non-Conforming'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid ""
"You don't conform to conventional expressions of masculinity or feminity."
msgstr "你不遵循傳統的男性或女性表達方式。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Non-Binary"
msgstr "性別：非二元"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Non-Binary'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "You express yourself as both feminine and masculine."
msgstr "你同時表達女性和男性的特徵。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Cis"
msgstr "性別：順性別"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Cis'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "You express the gender assigned at birth."
msgstr "你表達出生時被指定的性別。"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Trans-male"
msgstr "性別：跨性別男性"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Trans-female"
msgstr "性別：跨性別女性"

#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid "Gender: Agender"
msgstr "性別：無性別"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gender: Agender'}
#: .\traits\gender.json
msgid ""
"You express characteristics of both the male and female gender or don't "
"follow the normal gender normals or don't care to align to a gender."
msgstr "你表達男性和女性兩種性別的特徵，或不遵循正常的性別規範，或不關心與某個性別對齊。"

